{"title":"0019. 删除链表的倒数第 N 个节点","date":"2020-01-14T16:30:45.158Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 15, 2020","L":"01/15/2020","MM-DD":"01-15"},"updated":"2020-01-14T16:30:45.158Z","content":"<p><a href=\"leetcode/0019-en\">English</a>｜ 简体中文</p>\n<h2 id=\"题目描述\">题目描述<a href=\"leetcode/0019#题目描述\"></a></h2><p>给定一个链表，删除链表的倒数第 <em>n</em> 个节点，并且返回链表的头结点。</p>\n<p><strong>示例：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>给定一个链表：<strong>1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5</strong>，和 <strong><em>n</em> = 2</strong>。</p>\n<p>当删除了倒数第二个节点后，链表变为 <strong>1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;5</strong>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>说明：</strong></p>\n<p>给定的 <em>n</em> 保证是有效的。</p>\n<p><strong>进阶：</strong></p>\n<p>你能尝试使用一趟扫描实现吗？</p>\n<h2 id=\"题解\">题解<a href=\"leetcode/0019#题解\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">2</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">removeNthFromEnd</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"number\">_</span> head: ListNode?, <span class=\"number\">_</span> n: Int)</span></span> -&gt; <span class=\"type\">ListNode?</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">3</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> p = <span class=\"type\">ListNode</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">4</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        p.next = head</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">5</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> q = p, r = p</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">6</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"number\">_</span> <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>..&lt;n &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">7</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            q = q.next!</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">8</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">9</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> q.next != <span class=\"literal\">nil</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">10</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            q = q.next!</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">11</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            r = r.next!</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">12</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">13</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        r.next = r.next?.next</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">14</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> p.next</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">15</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">16</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","link":"leetcode/0019","plink":"https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0019/","toc":[{"title":"题目描述","id":"题目描述","index":"1"},{"title":"题解","id":"题解","index":"2"}],"copyright":{"author":"FiTeen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0019/\" title=\"0019. 删除链表的倒数第 N 个节点\">https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0019/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}